text
@Libchamplain is a C library providing a ClutterActor that displays maps
such as OpenStreetMap.  You can also have markers.  These markers can be
animated or not and are interactive. Libchamplain-gtk is a Gtk+ widget
that wraps around libchamplain's ClutterActor.
@


